## Cluster Composition (Each Environment)

- 1 Rancher Server (dedicated)
- 1 HAProxy Load Balancer
- 3 Control Plane nodes
- 3 Worker nodes
- 4 GPU nodes
- **Total: 12 hosts per environment**

